---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

import ContactCTA from '../components/ContactCTA.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About | Jeanine White" description="About Jeanine White Lorem Ipsum">
	<div class="stack gap-20">
		<main class="wrapper about">
			<Hero
				title="About"
				tagline="Thanks for stopping by. Read below to learn more about myself and my background."
			>
				<img
					width="1553"
					height="873"
					src="/assets/at-work.jpg"
					alt="Jeanine White at work with a colleague"
				/>
			</Hero>

			<section>
				<h2 class="section-title">Background</h2>
				<div class="content">
					<p>
						Le Vinh Khang has a strong background in the tech industry. With a diverse and extensive portfolio, he has successfully worked on a wide range of projects, including web and mobile app development, UI/UX design, and content editing. His background reflects a deep understanding of technology trends, design principles, and editorial standards, making him a versatile professional in the field. Khang's experience and background have positioned him as an industry leader, capable of delivering innovative and strategic solutions that drive success in today's competitive digital landscape.
					</p>
					
				</div>
			</section>
			<section>
				<h2 class="section-title">Education</h2>
				<div class="content">
					<p>Le Vinh Khang is currently pursuing his education at <a href="https://thptgiongongto.hcm.edu.vn/">Giong Ong To High School</a>. Despite his young age, he has already demonstrated remarkable skills and accomplishments in the fields of development, design, and editing. His dedication to learning and his ability to apply his knowledge effectively are indicative of a bright future ahead. As he continues to grow and develop his talents, his education at <a href="https://thptgiongongto.hcm.edu.vn/">Giong Ong To High School</a> provides a solid foundation for his academic and professional journey</p>
				</div>
			</section>
			<section>
				<h2 class="section-title">Skills</h2>
				<div class="content">
					<p>Le Vinh Khang possesses an impressive array of skills that span across various programming languages and technologies. His skill set includes proficiency in <a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTML">HTML</a>, <a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/javascript">JavaScript</a>, <a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS">CSS</a>, <a href="https://autoitscript.com">AutoIt</a>, <a href="https://python.org">Python</a>, <a href="https://svelte.dev">Svelte</a>, <a href="https://astro.build">Astro</a> and <a href="https://dart.dev">Dart</a>. This diverse skill set not only showcases his versatility but also his ability to adapt to different development and design challenges. Le Vinh Khang's proficiency in these languages equips him with the tools necessary to excel as a developer, designer, and editor, making him a valuable asset in the industry.
					</p>
				</div>
			</section>
		</main>

		<ContactCTA />
	</div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
	.about {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 3.5rem;
	}

	img {
		margin-top: 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 1.5rem;
		box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
	}

	section {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 0.5rem;
		color: var(--gray-200);
	}

	.section-title {
		grid-column-start: 1;
		font-size: var(--text-xl);
		color: var(--gray-0);
	}

	.content {
		grid-column: 2 / 4;
	}

	.content :global(a) {
		text-decoration: 1px solid underline transparent;
		text-underline-offset: 0.25em;
		transition: text-decoration-color var(--theme-transition);
	}

	.content :global(a:hover),
	.content :global(a:focus) {
		text-decoration-color: currentColor;
	}

	@media (min-width: 50em) {
		.about {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: 1fr 60% 1fr;
		}

		.about > :global(:first-child) {
			grid-column-start: 2;
		}

		section {
			display: contents;
			font-size: var(--text-lg);
		}
	}
</style>
